
                                    HOW TO RUN AND USER THE PROJECT


1.We can open the project by double clicking on cmd.bat file this will automatically run the commands for local server
2.Now in browser paste the url http://localhost:1000/index for visiting the actual site
3.For visting the login page you can click on login menu or through url http://localhost:1000/login
4.For Register user there is also a link for registration in login page as well as through url http://localhost:1000/registration
there is two step layout for registration 1 for basic info and other for 3 security question
5 For visiting the profile page either through login button or through url http://localhost:1000/profile
6.In profile page you can see you your basic info and there is a logout button for redirecting the user back to login